{"questionId":"11273","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">Deuterium, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{}_1^2{\\text{H}}\">\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, undergoes fusion according to the following reaction.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{}_1^2{\\text{H}} + {}_1^2{\\text{H}} \\to {}_1^3{\\text{H}} + {\\text{X}}\">\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">→</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>X</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">The following data are available for binding energies per nucleon.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{}_1^2{\\text{H}} = 1.12{\\text{MeV}}\">\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1.12</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>MeV</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{}_1^3{\\text{H}} = 2.78{\\text{MeV}}\">\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>H</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2.78</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>MeV</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">Determine, in MeV, the energy released.</span></p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana , Arial , Helvetica , sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">«3 x 2.78&nbsp;− 2&nbsp;× 2 × 1.12»<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana , Arial , Helvetica , sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">See 3 × 2.78/8.34 <em><strong>OR</strong> </em>2 × 2 × 1.12/4.48✔<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana , Arial , Helvetica , sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">3.86 «MeV» ✔</span></p>\n<p style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana , Arial , Helvetica , sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;white-space:normal;\">&nbsp;</p>","meta":{"questionId":"11273","referenceCode":"19M.2.SL.TZ2.6bi","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Determine, in MeV, the energy released.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"bi","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLa